name: Anomaly - 041
description: Everything that comes into contact with Anomaly - 002, their properties change within a 10 meter radius.   Take this Silvertip Reef Shark,   tests suggest that it's not even sentient, as inanimate as synthetic plastic, and yet it behaves as if it's alive, continuing on it's daily activities as if it were it's original form, albeit with a highly altered appearance.
